  <refsection id="Description_TEXT_f">
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>
	This special block is only use to add text at any point of the diagram
	window. It has no effect on the simulation.   
	</para>
    <para>
      Starting from Scilab 5.2, it is possible to write <link
      linkend="math_rendering_features_in_graphic">LaTeX or MathML
      expression</link>.
    </para>

  </refsection>
  <refsection id="Dialogbox_TEXT_f">
    <title>Dialog box</title>
    <para>
      <inlinemediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="../../../../images/gui/TEXT_f_gui.gif" align="center" valign="middle"/>
